<p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;为贯彻“创业创新，知识管理”的校训，坚持“三好一专，十一工程”培养理念，表彰先进、培树典型、激励奋进，进一步促进我校班风、学风 、校风建设。12月9日晚6：30经济管理学院组织开展2023—2024学年“先进班级答辩会”，其中参与“优良学风班级”评选的班级共有5个，参与“先进班集体”评选的班级共有7个。出席本次评选的评委有：学工办主任郭伟老师、辅导员钟宝乐老师、丁瑞风老师、杨磊老师。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971278868044708.png" title="1733971278868044708.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103049.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">评选过程</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 活动正式开始，此次评选分设“优良学风班级”和“先进班集体”两项荣誉，班级代表们依次上场，展示各自所在班级的优良班风、学风及先进事迹、所获荣誉。评委老师结合选手展演内容及现场表现进行综合评分。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971297329032963.png" title="1733971297329032963.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103055.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B230509</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971315375055431.png" title="1733971315375055431.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103101.png"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B220507</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971338988048228.png" title="1733971338988048228.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103107.png"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B230503</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971363928037903.png" title="1733971363928037903.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103112.png"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B230508</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971383074008229.png" title="1733971383074008229.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103116.png" width="628" height="482" style="width: 628px; height: 482px;"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B220505</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971408177096790.png" title="1733971408177096790.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103121.png"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B220508</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971424642099438.png" title="1733971424642099438.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103125.png"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B230505</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971439775097981.png" title="1733971439775097981.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103130.png"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B220502</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971456902088614.png" title="1733971456902088614.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103135.png"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B230502</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971475873053518.png" title="1733971475873053518.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103141.png"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B220503</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971493592083737.png" title="1733971493592083737.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103147.png"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B220511</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 评委老师们认真聆听了每位班级代表的总结汇报，并针对每位代表的发言提出了精确的问题。他们对班级代表们在汇报中展现的亮点予以肯定，也直接指出了存在的不足，给出了建设性的反馈和建议。评委老师们的点评深入而细致，极大地促进了班级代表们对班级建设和管理的深刻理解和改进。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241212/1733971511715071556.png" title="1733971511715071556.png" alt="微信图片_20241212103153.png"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 此次先进班集体评选，充分展示了经管学子在助力班集体发展方面的良好表现，充分肯定了各班级长期以来的辛勤付出与卓越成就，更为我院其他班级提供了可借鉴的宝贵经验。我院学子也将继续以更加饱满的热情、更加扎实的行动，投入到班级建设中去，共同书写学院发展新篇章。</span></p><p><br/></p>